channel.title: Error j5 Connect [WILL REP+ FOR HELP]
channel.description:
Alright, i know theres already a topic for this but i have a different error. I have a client.java, so i change the ip in there from 127.0.0.1 to my server ip. I dont have a Loader.java nor go i have a Gui/EGui. I know for a fact my server is online because i can connect with other clients but its very buggy, thats why i dont use them. This is a 525 and im using DannySkape525 Client. I need to change the up but i have no idea how to, and when i try to run my client i get the error in my title. If anyone can help me ill Rep. Thanks.
[NOTE] Idk if this is the right place, people in Client Help told me not to post there so i post here. Thanks again!
